fields.description:
To evaluate EUCA-11117, I've created 20 CF stacks for 100 IAM accounts. A simple CF template is used that is to create a bucket (see below). The bash loop used to create the stacks looks like this:

{code:java}
 for i in {1..100}; do acctname="acct$i"; echo $acctname; cd $acctname; source ./eucarc; for j in {1..20}; do euform-create-stack -p BucketName=bucket$acctname$j --template-file /root/spark/bucket.template mybucket$j; done; cd /root/accounts; done; 
{code}

When the script finishes, all stacks are in "CREATE_IN_PROGRESS" state and none of it makes any progress. Deleting stacks don't work as the state never changes from 'CREATE_IN_PROGRESS".


-------------
[root@b-03 spark]# cat bucket.template 
{
    "Parameters" : {
     "BucketName" : {
      "Description" : "Name of new bucket to be created",
      "Type" : "String"
    }
    },
    "Resources" : {
       "mybucket" : {
           "Type" : "AWS::S3::Bucket",
           "Properties" : {
              "BucketName" : { "Ref" : "BucketName" }
           }
       }
    }
}

comments.body:
[~spark], that is how euctl command works for properties that are known to be JSON:

{code}
#
# euctl cloudformation.swf_workflow_worker_config --format raw --dump
{ "DomainRetentionPeriodInDays": 1, "PollThreadCount": 8, "MaximumPollRateIntervalMilliseconds": 50 }
#
#
{code}

use the "dump" option with a "format" of "raw" to see output equivalent to the old euca-describe-properties command.

[~sjones] I ran the same bucket-creating CF template and created 2000 stacks. In the beginning, I saw about 300 stacks failing (due to timeout) per hour. Then about 16 hours later this morning, about 1000 stacks are stuck in CREATE_IN_PROGRESS (and 300 in ROLLBACK_IN_PROGRESS).  Before running the benchmark, I've doubled the thread count in the property. There are 5 UFS in this scale setup. Is this behavior expected?

[root@a-02-l ~]#  euctl cloudformation.swf_activity_worker_config
cloudformation.swf_activity_worker_config = {"PollThreadCount": 16, "TaskExecutorThreadPoolSize": 32, "MaximumPollRateIntervalMilliseconds": 50 }

[root@a-02-l ~]#  euctl cloudformation.swf_workflow_worker_config --format raw --dump
{
  "MaximumPollRateIntervalMilliseconds": 50, 
  "DomainRetentionPeriodInDays": 1, 
  "PollThreadCount": 32
}
